description: If you want me to automatically kick or ban members after a certain number of warnings, you can do so here
noKickAnymore: {emotes.success} | Members will no longer be automatically kicked
noBanAnymore: {emotes.success} | Members will no longer be automatically kicked
autoKick: {emotes.success} | Members will be kicked automatically on {count} warnings from now on
autoBan: {emotes.success} | Members will be automatically banned with {count} warnings
